{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA Gohdiba\nzehlahs no Pilsjahta Widdus/\nun stahweja us to Kalnu/ kas\ntam Pilsjahtam prett Rihteem\nbiia."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad vazehle manni tas\nGars/ un wedde manu eekſch\nParahdiſchanas/ un zaur to\nDeewa Garru us Kaldeju pee\nteem Aiswesteem/ un ta Paraſch-\nDiſchana/ fo es biu redſejs/ us-\nkahpe no mannim."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es runnaju teem Ais-\nwesteem wiſſus Wahrdus ta\nKUNGA/ fo wiſſch man bij\nparahdtjs."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XII. Nodalla.\nEzekiels falassa fauws Rihkus: 1/ 2. Lau-\nschaß ar aisſectahm Azzim zaar weenu See-\nnu: 5 Par Sihmi/ ka Zidekiſum tam Reh-\nniram no Jerusalemes ta buhs behgt/ un\napſtulbotam us Babeli weſsam tapt: 8/ 10.\nEhd fauw Maiſi ar Drebbeſchanas/ un dſer\nfatu Uhdeni ar Tribjeſchanas: 17/ 18. Par\nSihmi to nahkuſchu Behdu eekſch Jerusa-\nlemes: 19. Un tad mitteſees winnu faſka,\nmee Wahrdi: 21/ 22.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta KUNga Wahrdē\nnotikke us man/ kas faz-\nzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrns/ tu\ndsihwo ſtarp weenu pahrgalwi-\ngu Nammu/ kam Azzis irr re-\ndseht/ bet tee ne reds/ ſain Autis\nirr dsirdeht/ bet tee ne dsird/ jo\ntee irr weens pahrgalwigs Nams."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz tu Zilweka Behrns/\ntaisajs Aisweſchanas Rihkus/\nun aiseij patchā Deenā preekſch"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "was Weetas us zittu Weetâ\npreekſch winnu Azzim/ jaſchu t\nfainannihg/ ka tee weens pah-\ngalwigś Nams irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz iſneess tawus Ri-\nkus/ itt ka Aisweſchanas Rihtā\npaſchā Deenā preekſch winnu A-\nzim/ un tad tu iſeij Walkā-\npreekſch winnu Azzim/ itt ka t\niſeet/ kas aiswesti tohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rohz zaur to See-\npreekſch winnu Azzim/ un iſne-\n(tawus Rihtus) zaur winn\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Preekſch winnu Azzī-\nbuhs tew tohs us Plezzehtm ne-\nPakrehſlibā buhs tew tohs\nnest/ tawu Waignu buhs te-\napſegt/ ka tu to Semini ne re-\nJo es efmu tewi tam Israē-\nNammam par Brihnunu lizz\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es darriju ta/ ka m\nbiia pawehlehts/ es iſneffu-\nwus Rihtus Deenā itt ka Ri-\nkus to/ kas aiswesti tohp/\nWalkara rakku eſtewi zaur S-\nnu ar Rohku. Es iſneffu te-\nPakrehſlibā/ un nefſu tohs\nPlezzehtm preekſch winnu. Z-\nzim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rihtā notikke ta KU-\nGA Wahrdē us man/ kas ſ-\nzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrns/ ta-\ns Israēta Namē/ tas pa-\ngalwigś Nams ne irr us tew-\nzijs: Ko darri tu?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakki us teem: Ta fa-\ntas KUNgs KUNGS: Sc-\nNasta irr tas Jerusalemes Le-\nKu-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
